@Deprecated public class DelayedRegionOverlapAssociation extends DelayedRegionOverlapAssociation
Deprecated.
Use DelayedRegionOverlapAssociation instead. This class is mis-packaged.
Determines that the association to a region is OWNER if the input region is in a set of source regions.

This class only performs a spatial query if its DelayedRegionOverlapAssociation.getAssociation(List) method is called.
